      "title": "Power outages will last for one hour",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Chairman of the Public Utilities Commission Mr. Janaka Ratnayake said today (5) afternoon that the power cut has been reduced to one hour from tomorrow (6) and the said power cut will be in effect until the 9th of this month.",
        "Accordingly, Mr. Janaka Ratnayake further mentioned that power cuts will be implemented from 6.00 pm to 9.00 pm in 20 zones from 'A' to 'W'."
      ],
